snippet.title: Taxi Life: A City Driving Simulator | Management Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Taxi Life isn't just about driving customers to their destination, it's also about creating and managing your own taxi company in Barcelona.

Buy new cars with the profits from your fares! Hire employees based on their profile and assign them to cars, neighbourhoods and time slots. Make the right decisions to maximize your profits.

Taxi Life: A City Driving Simulator will be available on March 7th, 2024 on Xbox Series X|S, PlayStation 5 and PC.

Pre-order Taxi Life: A City Driving Simulator and get your unique convertible Taxi! 

🚖 Playstation 👉 nacon.me/PreorderTaxiPS
🚖 Xbox 👉 nacon.me/PreorderTaxiXbox
🚖 Wishlist on Steam 👉 nacon.me/TaxiLifeSteam
